0:{"rsc":["$","$1","c",{"children":[["$","$L2",null,{"title":"宇宙のイベント行ってきた","level":3,"levelTitle":"リアル体験","logo":"CBittekita","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"glass-card rounded-xl p-8 mb-8","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"flex items-start gap-4 mb-6","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"p-3 rounded-lg bg-primary/20","children":["$","svg",null,{"xmlns":"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg","width":24,"height":24,"viewBox":"0 0 24 24","fill":"none","stroke":"currentColor","strokeWidth":2,"strokeLinecap":"round","strokeLinejoin":"round","className":"lucide lucide-camera w-8 h-8 text-primary","aria-hidden":"true","children":[["$","path","18u6gg",{"d":"M13.997 4a2 2 0 0 1 1.76 1.05l.486.9A2 2 0 0 0 18.003 7H20a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v9a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H4a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V9a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h1.997a2 2 0 0 0 1.759-1.048l.489-.904A2 2 0 0 1 10.004 4z"}],["$","circle","1vg3eu",{"cx":"12","cy":"13","r":"3"}],"$undefined"]}]}],["$","div",null,{"children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-2","children":"行けなかったイベントの熱量と空気を、あなたのお手元へ。"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed space-y-3","children":[["$","p",null,{"children":"日程や場所の都合で参加できなかったイベントの様子を、運営メンバーが代わりに体験し、レポートとして不定期でお届けするコンテンツです。どんな議論があったのか、分かりやすく整理して発信します。"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"単なる情報まとめではなく、会場の雰囲気や参加者の熱量など、実際に行ったからこそ分かる「その場の体験」を持ち帰れるのが特徴です。遠方の方や予定が合わなかった方も、リアルな空気感を感じることができます。"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"日々進む宇宙の世界の“今”を知ることは、とても刺激的な体験です。レポートを読むことが「次は行ってみたい」というモチベーションにもつながります。少しだけのぞいてみる感覚で、気軽にお楽しみください。"}]]}]]}]]}]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-8","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"glass-card rounded-xl p-6","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"flex items-center gap-3 mb-4","children":[["$","svg",null,{"xmlns":"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg","width":24,"height":24,"viewBox":"0 0 24 24","fill":"none","stroke":"currentColor","strokeWidth":2,"strokeLinecap":"round","strokeLinejoin":"round","className":"lucide lucide-c